{"tid":350161,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[JS3480] 語言、文化及傳意廣泛學科oday之你問我答","createTime":"2017-08-07T04:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T08:57:46.000Z","uid":134065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1662e6756b1c54a2d5691031eb8a6dfd309ed4b3","tid":350161,"uid":134065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:52:00.000Z","msg":"欸～放Jupas啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！有無巴絲收到JS3480語言、文化及傳意廣泛學科 (Broad Discipline of Language, Culture and Communication) 嘅offer呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小弟都係讀呢科，今年year 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話咁快就過左一年，諗翻起上年做freshmen個陣懵剩剩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩都唔識，又唔知呢科讀乜，又唔知poly oday係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我都好體會到各位巴絲嘅感受嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我開翻個post同大家講下oday係點架啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱先check過今年放jupas係8月7號，咁你地check完jupas offer，確認左係JS3480之後呢，你就要記得係第二日(即係8月8號)下午五點之前交翻$5000留位費，如果唔係就無U讀架啦！Poly嘅registration係喺網上註冊，上翻eAdmission就可以註冊架啦，搞掂咗你就正式係一個大學生啦！恭喜曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到之後跟翻日子你就可以翻學校拎翻張學生證，記得要拎啊，因為poly好多地方都要學生證先入到架！ <br />\n<br />\nPoly嘅oday係會分3日搞嘅，而今年FH(Faculty of Humanities人文學院)嘅oday就會係8月13號，亦係唯一嘅途徑比freshmen報ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以記得要係個日報埋啦！oday 時間會係朝早9點到6點，大家可以係呢段時間之內翻poly～嚟到poly之後，你就要去一個叫VA嘅地方(即係邵逸夫樓)，先去VA119填學校同學生會比你嘅問卷，整埋學生會會員證。記住呢科(語言、文化及傳意廣泛學科)係poly嘅course code係03403，有人問起唔好再答jupas個JS3480喇，係唔同架！我上年都搞亂左，7到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞掂左佢地就會比張寫住 &ldquo;人文&rdquo; 兩隻字嘅貼紙你，之後就可以轉右去VA109-111行booth啦！我就記得一入去就已經見到雞乸咁大隻字寫住 &ldquo; 語言唯一OCAMP&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哇咁我見到唯一喎大佬，緊係喇喇臨報左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾問翻先知原來呢一科淨係得一個ocamp報，就係faculty搞嘅中O，所以如果想識自己同科嘅同學仔，就一定要報喇！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哎老啦！小弟今年都year2，自問自己都係一個小毒毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗左好耐都唔知報唔報ocamp好，睇其他巴絲啲post又話chur又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過諗翻轉頭都好彩有報到ocamp，先識到依家班同學兼死黨，一齊上堂食飯chur project，乜都抵曬啦！真係好彩有報到ocamp咋，先至無變成毒到無得再毒嘅小毒毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係non-jupas嘅freshmen，雖然唔會收到oday嘅email，但都可以帶埋online confirmation去oday報名，或者直接聯絡翻ocamp嘅相關負責人都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大學4年係一段寶貴嘅日子，希望入到嘅各位都可以有一個充實嘅ulife，過3爆4啦!!!   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd41a1dce328d312fdd0be2494af862770db11cf","tid":350161,"uid":103414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"哇巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cca0484f12bd07d6d639a13f923cbb5be86f5db","tid":350161,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"係咪有得揀中英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打揀左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求其放左a3碌入左但完全唔知讀啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aefddc48308e8891441a2c7b5573aeb43a1c143","tid":350161,"uid":81364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有得揀中英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打揀左咩<img src=\"/